<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>End of the Month Outreach & Charity Series | EHI</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --green-deep: #0a3d2e;
      --green-mid: #145c3f;
      --green-bright: #1e8a57;
      --green-light: #2eb872;
      --gold: #d4a42a;
      --gold-light: #f0c84e;
      --cream: #faf6ee;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text-dark: #0d1f17;
      --text-mid: #2d4a38;
      --text-muted: #6b8c78;
      --border: rgba(20,92,63,0.15);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 18px 5%;
      background: rgba(10,61,46,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,164,42,0.3);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--white); font-weight: 300; }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--green-deep) !important;
      padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 2px;
      font-weight: 600 !important;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light) !important; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--green-deep) 0%, var(--green-mid) 55%, #0e4a32 100%);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      padding-top: 80px;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 70%, rgba(46,184,114,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 80% 20%, rgba(212,164,42,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
    }
    /* decorative circle */
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 520px; height: 520px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,164,42,0.15);
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 820px; padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(212,164,42,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,164,42,0.4);
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 18px; border-radius: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.15s ease both;
    }
    .hero h1 em {
      font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-light);
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.2rem);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 40px;
      line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
    }
    .hero-btns {
      display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.45s ease both;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--green-deep);
      padding: 14px 36px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em; transition: all 0.2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-outline {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      color: var(--white); padding: 14px 36px;
      font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em; transition: all 0.2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--gold-light); color: var(--gold-light); }

    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; bottom: 36px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      animation: float 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hero-scroll::after {
      content: '';
      width: 1px; height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
    }

    /* ── STATS ── */
    .stats-strip {
      background: var(--green-deep);
      padding: 32px 5%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
      gap: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,164,42,0.2);
    }
    .stat-item {
      text-align: center; padding: 20px 16px;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--gold-light); line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
    section { padding: 96px 5%; }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green-bright); margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section-body {
      font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 1.8; max-width: 620px;
    }

    /* ── ABOUT ── */
    .about { background: var(--white); }
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px; align-items: center;
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .about-img-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-img-wrap::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -16px; left: -16px;
      right: 16px; bottom: 16px;
      border: 2px solid var(--gold);
      border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0;
    }
    .about-img-wrap img {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      width: 100%; border-radius: 4px;
      display: block;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(10,61,46,0.2);
    }
    .about-img-placeholder {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-mid), var(--green-bright));
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.9rem;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .about-img-placeholder svg { opacity: 0.4; }

    /* ── WHAT WE DO ── */
    .what-we-do { background: var(--cream); }
    .wwd-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .wwd-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px; }
    .wwd-header .section-body { margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px; padding: 36px 32px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green-bright), var(--gold));
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(10,61,46,0.1); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .card-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30,138,87,0.1), rgba(30,138,87,0.05));
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,87,0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* ── IMPACT ── */
    .impact {
      background: var(--green-deep);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .impact::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px;
      width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212,164,42,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }
    .impact-inner {
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px;
      align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .impact .section-label { color: var(--gold-light); }
    .impact .section-title { color: var(--white); }
    .impact .section-body { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
    .impact-list { margin-top: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    .impact-item {
      display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .impact-dot {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; min-width: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(212,164,42,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,164,42,0.4);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--gold-light); margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .impact-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); line-height: 1.6; }
    .impact-quote {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
      padding: 36px; border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .impact-quote blockquote {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .impact-quote cite {
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gold-light);
      font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── SUPPORT CTA ── */
    .support {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-mid) 0%, var(--green-deep) 100%);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .support .section-label { color: var(--gold-light); }
    .support .section-title { color: var(--white); margin: 0 auto 20px; }
    .support .section-body { margin: 0 auto 48px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-align: center; }
    .support-ways {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 48px;
    }
    .support-way {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 28px 20px; border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--white); transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .support-way:hover {
      background: rgba(212,164,42,0.12);
      border-color: rgba(212,164,42,0.3);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    .support-way-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .support-way h4 { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .support-way p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.5; }
    .bank-info {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(212,164,42,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,164,42,0.3);
      padding: 20px 36px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 32px;
      color: var(--white); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .bank-info strong { color: var(--gold-light); }

    /* ── CONTACT ── */
    .contact-section {
      background: var(--cream);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px; margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .contact-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px 20px; border-radius: 4px;
      transition: all 0.2s; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .contact-card:hover { border-color: var(--green-bright); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .contact-card-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .contact-card h4 { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .contact-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--green-deep); font-weight: 500; word-break: break-all; }

    /* ── SOCIAL ── */
    .social-bar {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin-top: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .social-link {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 2px;
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--green-deep); transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .social-link:hover { background: var(--green-deep); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--green-deep); }
    .social-link svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: #040f0a;
      padding: 48px 5% 32px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      gap: 20px; text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 700;
    }
    .footer-tagline { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex; gap: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
    .footer-bottom {
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding-top: 20px; width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
      50%       { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-8px); }
    }
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .about-grid, .impact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .about-img-wrap { order: -1; }
      section { padding: 64px 5%; }
      .stats-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
      .stat-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">EHI <span>| Executives Helping Initiative</span></div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#programs">Programs</a></li>
      <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
      <li><a href="#support">Support</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.executivesinitiative.com" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">Visit EHI</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-badge">Monthly Community Initiative</span>
      <h1>End of the Month<br /><em>Outreach</em> &amp; Charity Series</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        At Executive Helping Initiative, service is intentional, consistent, and rooted in deep compassion. Every month, we step beyond words — showing up where help is needed most.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="#support" class="btn-primary">Support This Cause</a>
        <a href="#about" class="btn-outline">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll">Scroll</div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats-strip">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">30+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Orphanages Visited</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">20+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Communities Reached</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">1000+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Volunteers & Members</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">12+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Years of Service</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">Monthly</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Outreach Frequency</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="section-label">What Is EOTM?</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Turning Compassion <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--green-bright)">into Action</em></h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          End of the Month Outreach is EHI's signature community support initiative, carried out at the close of each month. It is a series of impactful visits and community engagements designed to uplift, support, and bring hope to underserved communities across Nigeria.
        </p>
        <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:16px;">
          The Charity Series is a flagship program within EHI designed to respond to urgent needs and uplift lives with strategic, compassionate action. Through these visits, we step beyond intention — not just with words, but with action.
        </p>
        <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:16px; font-style:italic; color:var(--green-bright);">
          These moments reflect who we are: people helping people with purpose, presence, and love.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-img-wrap reveal">
        <div class="about-img-placeholder">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
          <p>Community Outreach Moments</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROGRAMS -->
  <section class="what-we-do" id="programs">
    <div class="wwd-inner">
      <div class="wwd-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">Our Programs</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
        <p class="section-body">Five pillars of compassionate action that define every End of the Month Outreach visit — each one addressing a real, immediate need in our communities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-icon">🏠</div>
          <h3>Orphanage Visitation</h3>
          <p>We visit orphanages to shower children with love, supplies, and joy — restoring hope and showing every child they are valued and not forgotten.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Community Visits</h3>
          <p>Our teams go directly into underserved neighbourhoods, engaging residents and providing tangible support where it's needed most across Nigeria.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-icon">🏥</div>
          <h3>Medical & Welfare Support</h3>
          <p>We partner with health professionals to offer medical check-ups, welfare support, and health awareness to communities with limited access to care.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-icon">💊</div>
          <h3>Healthcare Support</h3>
          <p>From medicine donations to medical outreach events, we bring healthcare closer to the people who need it — with dignity and compassion.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-icon">🍱</div>
          <h3>Food Support</h3>
          <p>We distribute meals and food packages to families, orphanages, and communities — because no one should go hungry when we can help.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IMPACT -->
  <section class="impact" id="impact">
    <div class="impact-inner">
      <div class="reveal">
